summary:
Experienced business leader performing executive roles within the transport (aviation and rail) and heavy machinery (mining) industries. These businesses operate in highly regulated and competitive environments requiring inspirational leadership to ensure business objectives and values are understood and aligned with employee purpose. 

35 years experience in operations, engineering, design, planning, quality and reliability

Key competencies - inspirational leadership, coaching, defining purpose, business transformation and change, safety champion, process improvement
